      "excerpt" : "The quality improvement workshop for official journals of Trakya University was held on November 16-17, 2017 at Trakya University. The workshop for editors of eleven journals was conducted in collaboration with the...",
      "title" : "The quality improvement workshop for official journals of Trakya University has been held",
      "image" : "images/placeholder-news.jpg",
      "content" : "<p>\n\t<span><span>The quality improvement workshop for official journals of Trakya University was held on November 16-17, 2017 at Trakya University. The workshop for editors of eleven journals was conducted in collaboration with the Balkan Medical Journal.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>The opening speeches were made by Professor Cem Uzun, the president of the workshop and Editor-at-Large of Balkan Medical Journal, and Professor Erhan TabakoÄlu, Rector of Trakya University.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>Editors of Balkan Medical Journal shared their experiences with other Journal&rsquo;s editors. Following topics were presented and discussed;</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<span><span>How to improve journal quality? (Professor Cem Uzun)</span></span></li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<span><span>Scientific journal management and organization (Professor Zafer Ko&ccedil;ak)</span></span></li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<span><span>International scientific publishing standards (Professor Okan &Ccedil;alÄ±yurt)</span></span></li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<span><span>Relations between Editors and Journal owner (Professor Mustafa Ä°nan)</span></span></li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<span><span>Statistics and good reporting guidelines (Professor Necdet S&uuml;t)</span></span></li>\n\t<li>\n\t\t<span><span>Publication ethics (Professor Cem Uzun)</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<div>\n\t<span><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/01a.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/05a.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/10a.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/20a%281%29.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/21a.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/26a.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://balkanmedicaljournal.org/img/images/08a.jpg\" /></span></div>",
      "id" : 51,
      "featured" : false,
      "date" : ""
