      "excerpt" : "“Edirne Editor Workshop and Balkan Panel on Publication Ethics” , the 15th training events of Balkan Medical Journal took place on February 13 and 14, 2015 respectively. The meetings received the participation of...",
      "title" : "Edirne Editor Workshop and Balkan Panel on Publication Ethics Events Completed",
      "category" : "News",
